Installation in Firefox
-----------------------
Compile and move resulting .so to "$HOME/.mozilla/plugins". If the folder does not exists create it.

To check if the plugin is correctly installed go to page "about:plugins" in Firefox. It should appear in the list as "GStreamer Browser Plugin".

Debugging
---------
Launch from a shell closing previously opened browsers.

GST_DEBUG=gbp*:5 <browser>

e.g.: GST_DEBUG=gbp*:5 firefox

Sample HTML code for testing the plugin
---------------------------------------
<html>
<head>
<script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.3.2/jquery.js"></script>
<script text="text/javascript">
  $(function() {
    var player = $("#player")[0];
    player.uri = "file:///tmp/miaou.avi";
    player.start();
  });
</script>
</head>
<body>
<embed id="player" type="application/x-gbp"
    border="5"
    width="400"
    height="400"
    x-gbp-uri=""
/>

</body>
</html>
